fields.description:
Letting information:

Date available: 21/03/2015
Furnishing: Part-furnished
Deposit: £2769
Added on Rightmove: 18 March 2015 (9 minutes ago)

Full description

Property People are proud to present to the lettings market this spacious and beautiful 3 double bedroom, 2 bathroom maisonette with roof terrace, arranged over 2 floors.

The property boasts 2 large double bedrooms (one with fitted wardrobes), family bathroom and very spacious fully-fitted, modern kitchen/dining room on the first floor. The second/top floor has a further double bedroom, shower-room and stylish living room which gives access to a beautiful and large roof terrace measuring a generous 20ftx12ft (120 sq. ft. approx.) The roof terrace is east facing and has no obstruction on 3 sides and hence benefits from many hours of daylight.
